![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1578167594456-NBBXGWX6HYL2JGN7Y6LA/image-asset.jpeg?format=original)

With the Venom film moving ever closer, the guys get nostalgic and get back in the Delorean. The destination? 1994! Back when things were all that and a bag of chips, one of the most prolific cartoons based on a comic was born, with the debut of Spider-Man the Animated Series! The show educated an entire generation of wall crawling Spidey fans, and it was on THIS show that many got their first look at Venom and the alien suit in the  part story The Alien Costume. How does the story/show hold up close to 25 years later? You gotta listen to find out.

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
